    "en": {
      "name": "K9 - EX \"Werewolf\"",
      "effect": "2 Level 9 monsters\nWhile this card has material, it can attack a number of times each Battle Phase, up to the number of materials attached to it. When your opponent activates a card or effect (Quick Effect): You can detach 1 material from this card, then activate this effect depending on whose turn it is;\n\u25cf Yours: Banish 1 card your opponent controls and/or 1 card from their GY.\n\u25cf Your opponent's: Look at your opponent's hand and banish 1 card from it face-up until the End Phase.\nYou can only use this effect of \"K9 - EX \"Werewolf\"\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
